  <title>Resúmen di par di atministrado di window</title>

  <p>Ata'ki un diskripshon di e atministrado di windownan ku tin.</p>

  <section id="pros">
    <title>Marco</title>
    <p>Marco ta e atministrado di bentana standard di e MATE desktop environment. E ta hopi stabil i masha konfiabel mes. E por drai ku of sin e buffer pa e animashon di e desktop environment.</p>
    <p>If Marco is not installed already, you can install it with <cmd>apt install marco</cmd>.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="pros">
    <title>Metacity</title>
